@startuml DeviceStatusManager_Sequence_Heartbeat

title UML Диаграмма последовательностей: Обработка Heartbeat сообщения

actor "Брокер сообщений" as MessageBroker
participant "DeviceStatusManager" as DSM
participant "IMessageConsumer" as Consumer
participant "IDeviceRepository" as Repository
participant "IStatusEventPublisher" as Publisher
participant "DeviceStatus" as Status

MessageBroker -> Consumer: HeartbeatEvent(deviceId, timestamp)
activate Consumer

Consumer -> DSM: processHeartbeat(event)
activate DSM

DSM -> Repository: findById(deviceId)
activate Repository

Repository --> DSM: Optional<Device>
deactivate Repository

alt Устройство найдено
  DSM -> Status: updateLastSeen(timestamp)
  activate Status
  Status --> DSM: ok
  deactivate Status

  DSM -> Repository: save(device)
  activate Repository
  Repository --> DSM: ok
  deactivate Repository

  DSM -> Publisher: publishStatusChangedEvent(event)
  activate Publisher
  Publisher --> DSM: ok
  deactivate Publisher
else Устройство не найдено
  DSM -> DSM: log warning "Unknown device"
end

DSM --> Consumer: ack
deactivate DSM

Consumer --> MessageBroker: ack
deactivate Consumer

@enduml